NO RECORD MADE. Assistant District Attorney Daniel Bernard Deida appeared for the State. Attorney Francesco J Balistrieri in court for Adela Villarreal-Tellez. Defendant Adela Villarreal-Tellez in court. Clerk. M.Burke. Attorney Balistrieri advises he is working on an offer with the state.
Status conference scheduled for January 6, 2023 at 09:30 am.

Attorney Thomas Binger appeared for the State by zoom.  Defendant appeared in court in person and w/ Attorney Balistrieri.  Clerk. M.Burke. Court quashes authorization of warrant and does not forfeit bond. Attorney Balistrieri is working on an offer with the state and the DE is working on getting her DL. STC set to 10/31/22 at 1:30.
With Attorney Balistrieri a VA has been set to 07/08/22 at 9:00.

Attorney Dan Tombasco appeared for the State. Attorney Balistrieri appears on behalf of the DE who does not appear. Court forfeits bond and issues a $1,000 Bench Warrant. Stayed until 07/18/22 at 5:00.
No disposition. Leave on for next scheduled court activity.
